    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are consistent with MRL 2 scope and do not require assessment at this risk level. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions agree with experimental data within 18%, satisfying the RH < 1 acceptance criterion across all 5 operating points.",
